</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="14.[151,1436,152,551]" box="[198,995,450,476]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">
The name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Sars" authorityYear="1883" box="[322,449,450,475]" class="Malacostraca" family="Stenothoidae" genus="Metopa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="leptocarpa">
<emphasis box="[322,449,450,475]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">leptocarpa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
refers to the very long carpus on gnathopod 1.
</paragraph>
